tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE ReportData (
  report_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  report_name TEXT,
  report_date DATE,
  report_data JSONB
)

CREATE TABLE Visualizations (
    visualization_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    visualization_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    visualization_type VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    report_id INT NOT NULL,
    FOREIGN KEY (report_id) REFERENCES Reports(report_id)
);

CREATE TABLE reports (
  report_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  report_name VARCHAR(255),
  report_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE visualizations (
  visualization_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  visualization_name VARCHAR(255),
  visualization_type VARCHAR(50),
  visualization_data JSON
)

CREATE TABLE data_sources (
  data_source_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  data_source_name VARCHAR(255),
  data_source_type VARCHAR(50),
  data_source_conn_string VARCHAR(255)
)

CREATE TABLE aggregations (
  aggregation_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  aggregation_name VARCHAR(255),
  aggregation_type VARCHAR(50),
  aggregation_formula TEXT
)
